      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "崔秋山默然不语。朱安国道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "倪朱两人见他说得诚恳，忙道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "崔秋山道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱安国道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "倪浩道：",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们不妨直言相求，瞧他怎么说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "应松道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们有一件事，只有崔大哥帮得这个忙，因此上⋯⋯",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "崔秋山嗯了一声。应松道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_chong_huan",
      "speaker_name": "袁崇焕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位要他跟我学武？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "崔秋山道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
